tspan.tspan: Image Processing and Analysis (IPA), transforming raw image data into quantitative measurements, is an important part of
life sciences. However, as projects progress, IPA pipelines grow increasingly complex, involving the management of multiple
tools, versions, and dependencies, which can be a challenging task. To tackle this complexity, we introduce the IPA Project
Template. This template simplifies the initiation of new IPA projects and streamlines the reorganization of existing ones,
